'''Tasnilest''' d tussna i izerwen '''[[tameslayt]]''' akked '''[[tutlayt]]'''. [[Tasnilest]] temgarad ɣef [[tjeṛṛumt]] tamensayt imi, iswi n tussna-ya n yiles d asbadu n tutlayt. Ababat n Tesnilest nezmer ad d-nini d [[Ferdinand De Saussure]], dɣa, Segmi i d-yeffeɣ udlis-is umi i semman wid i t-id-yessufɣen Timsirin n tesnilest tamatut.

== Iḥricen d taɣulin tigejdanin n Tesnilest ==
* Tamsislit : D [[tussna]], tzerrew [[imesla]] i d-yettefɣen seg [[taɣuct]] n umdan ;
* Tasnimeslit : Tzerrew tawuri i [[Ila|lan]] yime<nowiki/>sla d y[[imeslic]]<nowiki/>en n yiwet n tutlayt ;
* Tasnalɣa : D tussna , tzerrew talɣiwin n wawalen Alɣac/Awalec ;
* Taseddast : Tzerrew amek i ttwasudsent tefyar gar-asent iwakken ad fɣent tefyar ;
* Tasnamka : Tzerrew [[anamek]] n w[[awal]] ;<span class="page_h"></span>

